itemap faq links contact us  corporate history group companies overseas group companies highlights ir calendar financials presentation annual report for shareholders corporate profile corporate principles corporate governance message from management management policy changes in capital rating and bond information home  about daiwa securities group  corporate history year event  commenced operations as fujimoto bill broker fujimoto bill broker bank  fujimoto bill broker converted to a stock corporation  fujimoto bill broker changed its corporate name to fujimoto bill broker bank  fujimoto bill broker bank changed its corporate name to fujimoto bill broker securities co ltd  fujimoto bill broker securities co ltd changed its corporate name to fujimoto securities co ltd  established daiwa securities co ltd by the merger of fujimoto securities co ltd and nippon trust bank  registered as securities firm based on the securities and exchange law  became a member of the tokyo osaka and nagoya stock exchanges  relocated main office to gofukubashi building gofukubashi building  established representative office in new york established daiwa asset management co ltd  listed on the second section of the tokyo osaka and nagoya stock exchanges transaction scenery  established representative office in london established local subsidiary in new york  granted license from the ministry of finance to operate as an integrated securities firm  launched nationwide online operation system ibm terminal  became underwriting manager for the first yen dominated bond issuance of asia development bank established local subsidiary in hong kong listed on the first section of the tokyo osaka and nagoya exchanges  became lead manager for the worlds first asian dollar bond development bank of singapore  established local subsidiary in singapore  issued first euroyen bond european investment bank  established local subsidiary in london  became lead manager for the first yen denominated bond issuance in the us market  launched hometrading services  became a registered member of the finance future exchange established daiwa institute of research ltd  listed on seven stock exchanges in europe  started sales of daiwa mmf  became the first listed company in japan to conduct buy back of shares after the amendment of the commercial law established local subsidiary in philippines  launched online brokerage service  introduced stock options system  finalized final agreement with the sumitomo bank ltd on setting up a joint venture company  daiwa securities co ltd became the first listed company in japan to move to a holding company structure and changed its corporate name to daiwa securities group inc established daiwa securities co ltd and daiwa sb investments ltd commenced opetarions as daiwa securities sb capital markets co ltd established local subsidiary in taiwan  daiwa securities sb capital markets co ltd changed its corporate name to daiwa securities smbc co ltd implementation of pc to front desks  daiwa securities launched  types of services daiwa consulting course and daiwa direct course  transited to a committee system introduced interim dividend system established daiwa smbcssc securities co ltd  daiwa securities group relocated main office to grantokyo north tower established local subsidiary in mumbai grantokyo north tower  daiwa institute of research ltd split to daiwa institute of research holdings ltd daiwa institute of research ltd and daiwa institute of research business innovation ltd  acquired close brothers corporate finance holdings ltd acquired jreit management company daiwa real estate asset management co ltd formerly known as kk davinci select daiwa securities group and sumitomo mitsui financial group decided to dissolve the joint venture in wholesale business  daiwa securities smbc co ltd changed its corporate name to daiwa securities capital markets co ltd  commenced daiwa next bank ltd  daiwa securities co ltd merged with daiwa securities capital markets co ltd about daiwa securities groupcorporate historygroup companiesoverseas group companies terms  conditions privacy policy disclosure policy daiwa securities group inc sitemap faq links contact us  corporate history group companies overseas group companies highlights ir calendar financials presentation annual report for shareholders corporate profile corporate principles corporate governance message from management management policy changes in capital rating and bond information  daiwa securities group inc has announced earnings results for q fy  notice of convocation of the th ordinary general meeting of shareholders is disclosed archives  report regarding consolidated capital adequacy ratio and consolidated leverage ratiosituation of soundness in management as of march    kb  daiwa securities group inc to acquire sagent advisors and signal hillsignificantly expands global ma advisory business  kb  daiwa pi to invest in frontiir pte ltd in singaporemyanmar  kb  position and policies concerning the reduction of the minimum investment unit  kb  preparation for establishing a new subsidiary in frankfurt germany  kb daiwa securities co ltd daiwa asset management co ltd daiwa institute of research holdings ltd daiwa institute of research ltd daiwa sb investments ltd daiwa securities business center co ltd daiwa property co ltd daiwa corporate investment co ltd daiwa institute of research business innovation ltd   overseas group companies   daiwa securities group inc has been selected as an index component of the ftse good index for the tenth year in a row daiwa securities group inc has been selected as an index component of the dow jones sustainability asia pacific indexes （djsi asia pacific） for the th year in a row   terms  conditions privacy policy disclosure policy daiwa securities group inc  for shareholders sitemap faq links contact us  corporate history group companies overseas group companies highlights ir calendar financials presentation annual re