and are listed on the shareholders list at the end of march are entitled to exercise voting rights at the ordinary general meeting of shareholders the th ordinary general meeting of shareholders was held on wednesday june   at the prince park tower tokyo in tokyo the th ordinary general meeting of shareholders notice of convocation of the th ordinary general meeting of shareholders   kb disclosed information on the internet in relation to the notice of convocation   kb fyi notice of convocation of the th ordinary general meeting of shareholders including disclosed information on the internet   kb  above two files are combined into one file for your convenience the notice of convocation of the th ordinary general meeting of shareholders was sent via postal mail on june   we disclosed the notice on the internet before mailing to provide the information to shareholders as swift as possible notice of results of exercise of voting rights at the th ordinary general meeting of shareholders  kb click here for prior reports investor relationshighlightsir calendarfinancialspresentationannual reportfor shareholdersshareholders meeting archive   how to view a pdf fileto view a pdf file you will need to have adobe reader installedto download a free copy of adobe reader click on the icon above terms  conditions privacy policy disclosure policy daiwa securities group inc  csr sitemap faq links contact us  corporate history group companies overseas group companies highlight ir calendar financials presentation annual report for shareholders corporate profile corporate principles corporate governance message from management management policy changes in capital rating and bond information home  csr october   csr report  updated  archives csr at daiwa securities group initiatives through business activities creating a rewarding workplace initiatives through npos and other organizations assistance to communities inside and outside of japan through foundations support for culture and the