on  am et view more businessweek news daiwa securities group inc  details daiwa securities group inc together with its subsidiaries primarily operates as a securities brokerdealer in japan and internationally the company operates in four segments retail wholesale asset management and investment it offers brokerage trading underwriting strategic advice product development and structured finance services the retail segment provides online and telephonebased securitiesrelated services through a network of  branches and sales offices as well as nonfacetoface channels including the internet and contact centers the wholesale segment offers sales and trading services of equities bonds foreign exchange and derivative products to customers such as institutional investors and corporations as well as underwriting services for equities and bonds initial public offerings and ma advisory services the asset management segment establishes and manages investment trusts for individual investors provides investment advisory services to pension funds and other institutional investors and manages assets the investment segment engages in the investment activities such as venture investments private equity investments corporate loan investments and energy investments the company is involved in the research and consulting activities and provision of information systems and other support functions the company was formerly known as daiwa securities co ltd and changed its name to daiwa securities group inc in  daiwa securities group inc was founded in  and is headquartered in tokyo japan detailed company description wwwdaiwagrpjp  employees last reported date  founded in  daiwa securities group inc  top compensated officers mr seiji nakata president chief executive officer  director age  total annual compensation ¥m mr nobuyuki iwamoto deputy president age  total annual compensation ¥m mr yoriyuki kusaki deputy president age  total annual compensation ¥m mr toshihiro matsui senior executive m